function.name: list_pop
function.brief: Removes and returns the last kld_list_node_t in the kld_list_t.

return.doc: kld_list_node_t in the passed in list.

argument.name: list
argument.doc: the list to pop the last element from.

function.name: list_shift
function.brief: Removes and returns the first kld_list_node_t in the kld_list_t.

return.doc: the first kld_list_node_t in the passed in kld_list_t

argument.name: list
argument.doc: the kld_list_t in which to remove the first kld_list_node_t from.
